These are the top five most mysterious, highly secretive and believed to be highly dangerous tribes in the entire world.
5. The New Guinea Tribes
This is the most diverse and highly organized tribe, they worship the god of death and there are numerous reports of human sacrifice and cannibalism.
4. The Fulani Tribe
Feared throughout their land due to their savage ways, for many years they were believed to be cannibals but that has been rectified in recent reports, but still many locals still fear them though most of them have known been absorbed to the modern world.
3. The Suma People
This Ethiopian tribe is still believed to be more than a thousand strong and still today resist any formal contact with the Ethiopian authorities, should they spot you in their land expect a lot of arrows coming your way, in very few cases in their history they have had alcohol and some modern luxurious so as diseases.
2. Mashco-Piro tribe, Peru
Unlike most tribes that exist today they are not that violent towards strangers but highly secretive and haven’t made outside contact for hundreds of years up until the Peruvian authorities made contact with them.
1. The Sentinelese
The Sentinelese people have caught the interests of millions of people around the world, they from North Sentinel Island in the Andaman Islands of India.
They are a highly isolated tribe, A National Geographic team tried to approach them and they were fiercely pushed back just after one of the team member got an arrow through his thigh, and two local guides were killed on sight.
Which other local tribes do you know off not mentioned in this article to be highly isolated and sometimes extremely dangerous? Please share your thoughts and opinions on the comment section down below.


